This directory holds the app, which lives in its own git repo.
Clone it here:

  gh repo clone dfp-side-hustle/app-conscious-pregnance app
  git clone git@github.com:dfp-side-hustle/app-conscious-pregnance.git app
  git clone https://github.com/dfp-side-hustle/app-conscious-pregnance.git app

Once cloned, app/ becomes the working tree of the app repo. This .gitkeep
file is the only thing under app/ tracked by the cowork meta repo; the
.gitignore ignores everything else (see app/* + !app/.gitkeep pattern).
